msContents.summary: Copy of a work on occult or hidden sciences (al-ʻulūm al-gharībah); 17 leaves attached to the manuscript with similar information added in different hands; numerous notes and marginal comments.

supportDesc.extent: ii, 125, ii leaves : 250 x 170 (200 x 110) mm, bound to 260 x 180 mm

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in naskh in black ink; pointed.

decoDesc.decoNote: Rubrications in red; numerous tables and some diagrams in red and black ink.

binding.p: Bound in worn black leather over pasteboard.

origin.p: Copy completed at the end of Dhū al-Qaʻdah in the year 866 AH (f. 107r).
